      "rationale": "Validation conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under bovine blood analog at clinically representative flow-speed combinations. Geometry fidelity to COU device assessed as high; fluid analog validated per ASTM F1841. Validation activities are directly representative of the COU."
