      "rationale": "Reynolds-Averaged Navier-Stokes with SST k-omega turbulence closure selected based on published benchmark comparisons for rotary blood pump flows. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied. Model form assumptions documented in simulation plan."
    },
